Package AI

Interface Summary
BuilderMachine Dynamic Objects that implement this interface are considered to be Builders.
BuildingOptions AI Classes that do implement this interface are can be considered as Builders units in the game.
ControllableUnit AI Classes that implement this interface will be considered controllable by either a Computer or Human opponent.
KillingOptions  
MainBuilding Dynamic Objects that implement this interface are considered main buildings;
TrainerOptions AI Classes that implement this interface will be considered as candidates to be used as Main Buildings.
WarMachine All Dynamic objects that implement this interface are considered candidates for Killer AI.
